page.text: eStark IT is a webpage created in WordPress that offers different graphic packs for start-ups. The project has apart form the home screen also 4 sub-screens informing about the company and each package. The different package solutions show some examples of what is included and offers a reasonable price. In the contact page the user can pick one of the selected packages and create and order or just leave a message.
